description:
This is a 7 minute workout called '6 Min Daily Pilates Abs Workout (No Equipment)' from the channel Jenna Collins Fitness.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Join me in this 6 minute Pilates abs workout. Its up to you whether you choose to perform this workout daily, a few times per week or mix it up with your other workouts.
